            Things changeâ€”in the world around us, in our hearts and minds, in our organizations, in what to work on, in how to work together, and how to deliver that work. Etsyâ€™s vice president of design Randy J. Hunt and CTO John Allspaw discuss the emergent and learned practices and behaviors that have enabled their teams to support one another and evolve together.
        
	
	
